thread.title: Emma

author: Emma
title: Emma
text:
Packaging was slightly beat up and had to be repaired by AusPost, but overall the product was around half the price I had paid previously with another company, so I was able to two instead.
The package also arrived in about 2 days, compared to over a week from the other company, despite AMR being interstate and the other 5 minutes down the road. Will definitely purchase through AMR again in the future, and recommend them to others.
